Principles
  Correct with delete/backspace
  No need to use space or return
  Number of letters
    3: default
    2+: ee cp op pi 
    1:
      calculator keys
        0-9 ~ .
        + - * / ^ ( ) =
      practical
        r/s: return
        lrn: ?
        inv: 
        sst: arrow-up
        bst: arrow-down

Primary
  A   B   C   D   E
  sec inv lnx ce  clr
  lrn xt  x2  vx  x1
  sst sto rcl sum ^
  bst ee  (   )   /
  gto 7   8   9   *
  sbr 4   5   6   -  
  rst 1   2   3   + 
  r/s 0   .   ~   =

Secondary
  vA  vB  vC  vD  vE
  se' in' log cp_ cl'
  pgm p>r sin cos tan
  ins cms exc prd ind
  del eng fix int abs
  pau x=t nop op_ deg
  lbl x>t sig avg rad
  stf iff dms pi_ gra
  wri dsz adv prt lst

Other (synthesized and indirect)
  hir rtn
  st* rc* su* pr* ex* pg* gt* op*
